d &#39;seeds&#39;, property &#39;textSource&#39;, property &#39;value&#39;. That now doesn&#39;t exist =
in your alternate, file-based seeds configuration. Eliminate the now unnece=
ssary override and the erre should go away.

(The Spring override mechanism=
s are powerful - since they let you group replacement values far from what =
they affect - and somewhat confusing, for the exact same reason.)

